        <title type="html"><![CDATA[sshfs on Win 10]]></title>
        <id>https://franklai.github.io/blog/2022/01/22/sshfs-on-win10</id>
        <link href="https://franklai.github.io/blog/2022/01/22/sshfs-on-win10"/>
        <updated>2022-01-22T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[又得遠端啦]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>又得遠端啦</p>
<p>這次嘗試用以下組合</p>
<ul>
<li>SSHFS-Win
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/billziss-gh/sshfs-win" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/billziss-gh/sshfs-win</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>WinFsp
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/billziss-gh/winfsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/billziss-gh/winfsp</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>SSHFS-Win Manager
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/evsar3/sshfs-win-manager" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/evsar3/sshfs-win-manager</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>用 SSHFS-Win Manager，有個 GUI 可以設定也是蠻方便的</p>
<p>自己用連線網路磁碟機，就有遇到路徑寫法問題</p>
<p>一般是寫 <code>\\sshfs\[LOCUSER=]REMUSER@HOST[!PORT][\PATH]</code></p>
<p>路徑是相對於 home path</p>
<p>要從根目錄開始的話，要用 sshfs.r</p>]]></content>
        <category label="Win10" term="Win10"/>
    </entry>
